# dataTypes

**Instance Property**

The types of data associated with the record.

## Declaration

```swift
@MainActor var dataTypes: Set<String> { get }
```

## Discussion

Each record contains the set of types that the associated website stores. For a list of possible types, see [doc://com.apple.webkit/documentation/WebKit/data-store-record-types].

## Getting the Data Type

- **Data Store Record Types**: Explore the constants that identify the types of data that websites store.
